Tost Grawlille 62674 BENER VALLEY Rb CHimicdm WA 9652 arg tl ee it. TT taeeons oF Sane eat HAY _ Manin, —: AS L_LWE_ \ 1 wes een ate
summary: Tost Grawlille grotesquely eats the world. The world is made up of people who want to eat each other. This is the human body. We are all made of the same material, and we all eat one another. Sane eat                HAY _ Manin, Man in, AS. As.
